### 验证token
POST {{host-sso}}:{{port}}/xxl-sso-server/app/logincheck?sessionId={{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

###

### 退出token登录
POST {{host-sso}}:{{port}}/xxl-sso-server/app/logout?sessionId={{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

###

